Regression is basically used for prediction

Types of regression
linear regression
polynomial regression
non linear regression

											Function
set of independent variables(x1,x2,x3) -=============>>>>> (output)dependent output

examples
------------------------
Demand forecasting
------------------------
 what is the differnce between classification and regression
 
 - in classification - assign a label for a new instance, categorical output
 - in regresion - Copute output value given the independent variables, a continuous output
 
 relationsip b/w input and output
  - usually a blackbox - in classification
  - a mathematical function - a regression problem
